Message:
What led me to learn
I had become a witch...?
I have no clue.

Before I knew it,
I had been abandoned...
and before I knew it,
I had been taken in.

A traveling circus just
happened to be in town.
Lively voices poured out
from inside the flashy tent.

It was so strange...
seeing people go in and out
with bright smiles on their faces.

After having stood outside
for the entire performance,
the circus troupe took me
in as one of their own.

That is pretty much
the first thing I remember.

Yes.
My entire life
began with the circus.
